y DI-62 IRMS. 16,17 Later, online techniques for volatile chlorinated 63 organics were developed measuring fragments of molecules of 64 compounds such as trichloroethene, dichloroethene, and vinyl 65 chloride using GC-IRMS. 18,19 Other recent approaches 66 included, for instance, the application of gas chromatography 67 quadrupole mass spectrometry (GCqMS) 20,21 and online 68 conversion to HCl for isotope ratio determination via GC-69 IRMS.},
